een reizend circus?

1
01:51:59,758 --> 01:52:00,466
Nu.

1
01:52:00,717 --> 01:52:01,800
Vooruit.

1
01:52:05,055 --> 01:52:08,515
Dori en Ori, tot uw dienst.

1
01:52:08,767 --> 01:52:09,350
Die...

1
01:52:09,601 --> 01:52:10,392
wil ik niet.

1
01:52:10,644 --> 01:52:11,894
Volkomen begrijpelijk.

1
01:52:16,650 --> 01:52:19,485
O, Fíli en Kíli.
Helemaal vergeten.

1
01:52:20,737 --> 01:52:22,988
O ja, en Nori, Bofur...

1
01:52:23,239 --> 01:52:24,948
Bifur...

1
01:52:26,409 --> 01:52:28,077
en Bombur.

1
01:52:29,204 --> 01:52:30,829
Is dat alles?

1
01:52:33,625 --> 01:52:35,125
Zijn er nog meer?

1
01:52:47,430 --> 01:52:51,183
Dus jij bent Eikenschild.

